avani/AFP/Getty</p></small></div></div></div><div class="sc-d9870e8f-0 bMtwqF"><div class="sc-d9870e8f-5 gKeKzI"><aside class="sc-d9870e8f-12 eWSurm"><div aria-hidden="true" class="rah-static rah-static--height-zero SidebarWrapper" style="height:0;overflow:hidden"><div><div class="sc-2e8621ab-0 jdutDe sc-d9870e8f-7 CYCPy"><a href="/users/sabrina-little" class="sc-2e8621ab-1 gnJVZv">Sabrina Little</a><span><p>is an assistant professor in the department of Leadership and American Studies at Christopher Newport University in Virginia, US. She also runs at an elite level and has been selected to represent the United States on five national teams. She is the author of <a href="https://academic.oup.com/book/55903" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer noopener"><em>The Examined Run</em></a><em> </em>(2024).</p></span></div><br/><div class="sc-d9870e8f-9 fVeAYS"><p>Edited by<a href="/users/nigel-warburton" class="sc-2e8621ab-1 gnJVZv">Nigel Warburton</a></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-95e65737-0 jmDajv"><span>3,300<!-- --> words</span><span class="sc-95e65737-1 cIhWyi"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" stroke="none" width="16" height="16" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" data-cy="icon-aeon-comment-bubble" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M21.303,16.553l1.107,3.783l-3.48-2.322c-0.689,0.234-1.422,0.371-2.193,0.371c-1.041,0-2.024-0.234-2.907-0.642 c2.034-1.697,3.333-4.275,3.333-7.166c0-1.994-0.625-3.836-1.677-5.347c0.406-0.073,0.823-0.117,1.251-0.117 c3.762,0,6.814,2.971,6.814,6.634c0,1.594-0.578,3.057-1.539,4.2L21.303,16.553z M15.255,10.684c0,3.861-3.213,6.99-7.176,6.99 c-0.812,0-1.583-0.144-2.31-0.391l-3.667,2.446l1.166-3.985l-0.744-0.638c-1.013-1.203-1.621-2.743-1.621-4.423 c0-3.858,3.215-6.987,7.176-6.987C12.042,3.696,15.255,6.825,15.255,10.684z"></path></svg><span>9<!-- --> <!-- -->comments</span></span><span class="sc-95e65737-2 gjbGGR"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" stroke="none" width="17" height