ow hues. A small figure of a child walks in the distance, casting a long shadow." loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-nimg="fill" style="position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent" sizes="(max-width: 640px) 100vw, (max-width: 960px) 45vw, (max-width: 1440px) 30vw, 430px" srcSet="https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/fc2aab27-79b1-4007-9a87-69bb7665ff8c/essay-and-so-it-goes-hr-v2-copy.jpg?width=256&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 256w, https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/fc2aab27-79b1-4007-9a87-69bb7665ff8c/essay-and-so-it-goes-hr-v2-copy.jpg?width=384&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 384w, https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/fc2aab27-79b1-4007-9a87-69bb7665ff8c/essay-and-so-it-goes-hr-v2-copy.jpg?width=640&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 640w, https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/fc2aab27-79b1-4007-9a87-69bb7665ff8c/essay-and-so-it-goes-hr-v2-copy.jpg?width=750&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 750w, https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/fc2aab27-79b1-4007-9a87-69bb7665ff8c/essay-and-so-it-goes-hr-v2-copy.jpg?width=828&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 828w, https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/fc2aab27-79b1-4007-9a87-69bb7665ff8c/essay-and-so-it-goes-hr-v2-copy.jpg?width=1080&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 1080w, https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/fc2aab27-79b1-4007-9a87-69bb7665ff8c/essay-and-so-it-goes-hr-v2-copy.jpg?width=1200&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 1200w, https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/fc2aab27-79b1-4007-9a87-69bb7665ff8c/essay-and-so-it-goes-hr-v2-copy.jpg?width=1920&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 1920w, https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/fc2aab27-79b1-4007-9a87-69bb7665ff8c/essay-and-so-it-goes-hr-v2-copy.jpg?width=2048&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 2048w, https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/fc2aab27-79b1-4007-9a87-69bb7665ff8c/essay-and-so-it-goes-hr-v2-copy.jpg?width=3840&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 3840w" src="https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/fc2aab27-79b1-4007-9a87-69bb7665ff8c/essay-and-so-it-goes-hr-v2-copy.jpg?